---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Now" description="What Michael Linder is doing now, inspired by nownownow.com.">
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">Now</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-muted">
      Last updated: May 2026 · Inspired by <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" class="underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-brand-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">nownownow.com</a>
    </p>

    <div class="prose mt-10">
      <h2>Professional</h2>
      <p>
        IT consulting and software architecture through <a href="https://strali.solutions" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Strali Solutions</a>. Focus: enterprise AI, Microsoft 365, DevOps.
      </p>

      <h2>Selected Projects</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Architecture consulting and AI advisory for a DAX-listed semiconductor company: RAG-based data integration, platform templates, UI concepts</li>
        <li>AI-assisted development with Claude Code and Copilot for faster delivery</li>
        <li>AI potential assessments and strategy for SMEs in the DACH region</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>AI Governance</h2>
      <p>
        Practical implementation of the EU AI Act for SMEs. Reading a lot, writing some of it down, talking to companies that want to understand what's coming.
      </p>

      <h2>Side Projects</h2>
      <p>
        This website. Building a personal knowledge base around AI Governance.
      </p>

      <h2>Personal</h2>
      <p>
        Amateur radio (OE8YML), mountains, family in Carinthia.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
